><span class="background-text background-text--2">1 Goal</span></div></div></div><div class="split-grid"><div class="split-grid__image"><div style="background-image: url(&quot;/assets/img/content/a631cf3c7abd8b04f71ae907dbe70cc4/objectively-focused.png&quot;)" class="background-image background-image--contain"></div></div><div class="split-grid__content"><div class="split-grid__text"><h2 class="heading">Objectively focused</h2><p>Making a successful website or application is more than just looking and feeling good, it requires tangible results. We believe that we should be super-accountable to our clients and that the objective way to achieve this is to set measurable targets that we collectively drive towards.</p><span class="background-text background-text--3">KPI</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main><footer role="contentinfo" class="main-footer"><div class="content-center content-gutter"><div class="main-footer__contact"><div class="grid"><div class="grid__item desktop-one-third"><h2 class="main-footer__heading">Talk to us</h2><p><a href="mailto:hello@clock.co.uk">hello@clock.co.uk</a><br><a href="tel:+441923261166">+44 (0)1923 261166</a></p></div><div class="grid__item desktop-one-third"><h2 class="main-footer__heading">Visit us</h2><address>The Old School House, Bridge Road, Hunton Bridge, Kings Langley, Hertfordshire. <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Clock+Limited/@51.6933143,-0.439069,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x487641ce2cdda103:0xb99b11bf84927c73!8m2!3d51.6933143!4d-0.4368803?hl=en">WD4&nbsp;8RQ</a></address></div><div class="grid__item desktop-one-third"><h2 class="main-footer__heading">Follow us</h2><div class="social-share"><a href="https://twitter.com/clock" class="social-share__link"><i class="icon icon--twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/clocklimited/" class="social-share__link"><i class="icon icon--facebook"></i></a><a href="http://uk.linkedin.com/company/clock-limited/" class="social-share__link"><i cla